        18
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baxter_Estates%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Baxter Estates earned Tree City USA status and is part of the Greater Port Washington area anchored by Port Washington.",
